Goon - Mafia
- Is part of the mafia team, and has the ability to check the role of a person, while simultaneously role blocking them for a particular night.
- Being part of the mafia, the Goon has permanent night protection.
- The goon performs his action in the morning, and receives the results during the night, along with the role-block happening in the night. The target is informed they were role blocked.
- Does not respawn.
